### ============================================================
### E-commerce API - Full test payloads
### ============================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5197
@token   = REPLACE_WITH_JWT
@adminToken = REPLACE_WITH_ADMIN_JWT

### --- ID cho test (đổi GUID tuỳ DB của bạn) ---
@userId       = 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
@productId    = 22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222
@categoryId   = 33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333
@orderId      = 44444444-4444-4444-4444-444444444444
@cartItemId   = 55555555-5555-5555-5555-555555555555
@couponId     = 66666666-6666-6666-6666-666666666666
@promotionId  = 77777777-7777-7777-7777-777777777777
@variantId    = 88888888-8888-8888-8888-888888888888


### ============================================================
### 1) AUTH
### ============================================================

### 1.1 Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "johndoe@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!",
  "confirmPassword": "SecurePassword123!"
}

### 1.2 Login (admin seeded sẵn)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@mebisoft.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 1.3 Refresh token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accessToken": "eyJhbGciOiJI...",
  "refreshToken": "replace_refresh_token_here"
}


### ============================================================
### 2) CART (user)
### ============================================================

### 2.1 Lấy giỏ hàng hiện tại
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.2 Sync giỏ guest → DB sau khi đăng nhập
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    { "productId": "{{productId}}", "quantity": 2 },
    { "productId": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222223", "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

### 2.3 Thêm item (RESTful)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "quantity": 2
}

### 2.4 Update số lượng item (Quantity=0 để xoá)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart/items/{{cartItemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 3
}

### 2.5 Xoá 1 item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart/items/{{cartItemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.6 Xoá toàn bộ giỏ
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.7 Apply coupon lên giỏ
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart/apply-coupon
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "couponCode": "WELCOME10"
}

### 2.8 Checkout toàn bộ giỏ (COD)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentMethod": 0,
  "cartItemIds": null,
  "shipping": null
}

### 2.9 Checkout - BankTransfer + shipping Ahamove
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentMethod": 1,
  "cartItemIds": null,
  "shipping": {
    "serviceId": "SGN-BIKE",
    "dropoff": {
      "lat": 10.762622,
      "lng": 106.660172,
      "address": "123 Lê Lợi, Quận 1, TP.HCM",
      "name": "Nguyễn Văn A",
      "mobile": "0909000001"
    },
    "items": [
      { "weight": 1.2, "length": 20, "width": 15, "height": 10, "description": "Hộp sản phẩm" }
    ],
    "routeOptimized": true,
    "note": "Giao giờ hành chính"
  }
}

### 2.10 Checkout - chỉ chọn subset cart items
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/cart/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentMethod": 2,
  "cartItemIds": [
    "{{cartItemId}}"
  ],
  "shipping": null
}


### ============================================================
### 3) ORDER (user)
### ============================================================

### 3.1 Chi tiết 1 đơn hàng của user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.2 Huỷ đơn hàng (owner, Pending/Confirmed, chưa thanh toán)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.3 Tạo shipment cho đơn (nested resource)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}/shipment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serviceId": "SGN-BIKE"
}


### ============================================================
### 4) PRODUCTS (public / user)
### ============================================================

### 4.1 Danh sách sản phẩm (filter + paging)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20&categoryId={{categoryId}}

### 4.2 Chi tiết sản phẩm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}

### 4.3 Liệt kê review sản phẩm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}/reviews?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10

### 4.4 Viết review (nested)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Sản phẩm tốt, đóng gói cẩn thận."
}


### ============================================================
### 5) ADMIN - ORDERS
### ============================================================

### 5.1 Liệt kê đơn (status=1 Confirmed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/orders?status=1&pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5.2 Liệt kê đơn theo khoảng ngày
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/orders?fromDate=2026-01-01T00:00:00Z&toDate=2026-12-31T23:59:59Z&pageNumber=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5.3 Chi tiết đơn (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5.4 Cập nhật trạng thái đơn: Confirmed | Cancelled | Completed
### OrderStatus: Pending=0, Confirmed=1, Cancelled=2, Completed=3, Delivering=4
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 1
}


### ============================================================
### 6) ADMIN - PRODUCTS
### ============================================================

### 6.1 Tạo sản phẩm
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sữa tắm MebiSoft 500ml",
  "description": "Sữa tắm dưỡng ẩm",
  "price": 150000,
  "stock": 100,
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "nameEn": "MebiSoft Body Wash 500ml",
  "descriptionEn": "Moisturizing body wash",
  "sku": "SKU-SBW-500",
  "slug": "sua-tam-mebisoft-500ml",
  "discount": 0,
  "unit": "chai",
  "unitEn": "bottle",
  "isActive": true,
  "productType": 0,
  "kind": 0,
  "buyType": 0,
  "priority": 10,
  "documentIds": [],
  "storeId": null
}

### 6.2 Update sản phẩm (id lấy từ URL, body không cần chứa Id)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "name": "Sữa tắm MebiSoft 500ml (updated)",
  "description": "Mô tả mới",
  "price": 165000,
  "stock": 80,
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "nameEn": "MebiSoft Body Wash 500ml v2",
  "descriptionEn": null,
  "sku": "SKU-SBW-500",
  "slug": "sua-tam-mebisoft-500ml",
  "discount": 5,
  "unit": "chai",
  "unitEn": "bottle",
  "isActive": true,
  "productType": 0,
  "kind": 0,
  "buyType": 0,
  "priority": 20,
  "documentIds": [],
  "storeId": null
}

### 6.3 Xoá sản phẩm
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### ============================================================
### 7) ADMIN - COUPONS
### ============================================================

### 7.1 Liệt kê coupon
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/coupons?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7.2 Chi tiết coupon
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/coupons/{{couponId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7.3 Tạo coupon (DiscountType: 0=Percentage, 1=FixedAmount)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/coupons
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "WELCOME10",
  "discountType": 0,
  "value": 10,
  "minOrderValue": 200000,
  "startDate": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "usageLimit": 1000
}

### 7.4 Tạo coupon giảm cố định 50k
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/coupons
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "SALE50K",
  "discountType": 1,
  "value": 50000,
  "minOrderValue": 300000,
  "startDate": "2026-04-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-06-30T23:59:59Z",
  "usageLimit": 500
}


### ============================================================
### 8) ADMIN - PROMOTIONS (PromotionRule)
### ============================================================

### 8.1 Liệt kê promotion
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/promotions?isActive=true&pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8.2 Chi tiết promotion
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/promotions/{{promotionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8.3 Tạo promotion - PercentageDiscount (Type=1)
### Target: 0=EligibleItems, 1=WholeOrder
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/promotions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rule": {
    "name": "Sale 15% tháng 4",
    "type": 1,
    "priority": 10,
    "startDate": "2026-04-01T00:00:00Z",
    "endDate": "2026-04-30T23:59:59Z",
    "isActive": true,
    "scope": {
      "productIds": null,
      "categoryIds": ["{{categoryId}}"]
    },
    "percentageAction": {
      "percent": 15,
      "target": 0
    },
    "buyXGetYAction": null
  }
}

### 8.4 Tạo promotion - BuyXGetY (Type=0)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/promotions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rule": {
    "name": "Mua 2 tặng 1",
    "type": 0,
    "priority": 20,
    "startDate": "2026-05-01T00:00:00Z",
    "endDate": "2026-05-31T23:59:59Z",
    "isActive": true,
    "scope": {
      "productIds": ["{{productId}}"],
      "categoryIds": null
    },
    "buyXGetYAction": {
      "buyProductId": "{{productId}}",
      "buyCategoryId": null,
      "buyQty": 2,
      "getProductId": "{{productId}}",
      "getCategoryId": null,
      "getQty": 1,
      "limitPerOrder": 3
    },
    "percentageAction": null
  }
}

### 8.5 Update promotion (id từ URL; body chỉ chứa rule)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/promotions/{{promotionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sale 20% tháng 4 (updated)",
  "type": 1,
  "priority": 15,
  "startDate": "2026-04-10T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-04-30T23:59:59Z",
  "isActive": true,
  "scope": {
    "productIds": null,
    "categoryIds": ["{{categoryId}}"]
  },
  "percentageAction": {
    "percent": 20,
    "target": 0
  },
  "buyXGetYAction": null
}

### 8.6 Xoá promotion
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/promotions/{{promotionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### ============================================================
### 9) ADMIN - VARIANTS
### ============================================================

### 9.1 Liệt kê variant theo productId
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/variants?productId={{productId}}&isActive=true&pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9.2 Chi tiết variant
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/variants/{{variantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9.3 Tạo variant
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/variants
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "sku": "SKU-SBW-500-RED",
  "price": 165000,
  "inventory": 50,
  "isActive": true,
  "options": [
    { "key": "color", "value": "red" },
    { "key": "size",  "value": "500ml" }
  ]
}

### 9.4 Update variant (id từ URL, body không cần Id)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/variants/{{variantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "SKU-SBW-500-RED-V2",
  "price": 170000,
  "inventory": 40,
  "isActive": true,
  "options": [
    { "key": "color", "value": "crimson" },
    { "key": "size",  "value": "500ml" }
  ]
}

### 9.5 Xoá variant
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/variants/{{variantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### ============================================================
### 10) PAYMENT - PAYOS
### ============================================================

### 10.1 Tạo link thanh toán PayOS (canonical)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payment/payos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "totalAmount": 280000000,
  "description": "Thanh toan don hang"
}

### 10.2 Webhook PayOS (canonical)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/webhooks/payos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "orderCode": 260417034039106,
    "amount": 280000000,
    "status": "PAID",
    "paymentLinkId": "8ed4922ccc074d579e97dfae1a3f08d3",
    "id": "evt-dev-001"
  },
  "signature": "REPLACE_WITH_SIGNATURE_FROM_GENERATE_CALL"
}


### ============================================================
### 11) SHIPPING (Ahamove)
### ============================================================

### 11.1 Ước lượng phí ship
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/shipping/estimate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderTime": 0,
  "path": [
    { "lat": 10.776889, "lng": 106.700806, "address": "Kho: 1 Nguyễn Huệ, Q1" },
    { "lat": 10.762622, "lng": 106.660172, "address": "123 Lê Lợi, Q1", "name": "Nguyễn Văn A", "mobile": "0909000001" }
  ],
  "services": ["SGN-BIKE"],
  "items": [
    { "weight": 1.2, "length": 20, "width": 15, "height": 10, "description": "Hộp sản phẩm" }
  ],
  "routeOptimized": true
}


### ============================================================
### 12) DEV TOOLS (chỉ chạy ở Development + role Admin)
### ============================================================

### 12.1 Sanity check admin role
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dev/sanity/admin-profile
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 12.2 Generate webhook payload đã ký
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dev/payos/webhook-simulator/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderCode": 260417034039106,
  "amount": 280000000,
  "status": "PAID",
  "paymentLinkId": "8ed4922ccc074d579e97dfae1a3f08d3",
  "id": "evt-dev-001"
}

### 12.3 Trigger webhook pipeline 1 phát (ký + chạy)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dev/payos/webhook-simulator/trigger
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderCode": 260417034039106,
  "amount": 280000000,
  "status": "PAID",
  "paymentLinkId": "8ed4922ccc074d579e97dfae1a3f08d3",
  "id": "evt-dev-trigger-001"
}

###
